.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-summary \- show payment counts and totals
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of total, complete, failed, and pending payments plus total amount sent.
.PP
Output: JSON object with total, complete, failed, pending, total_sent_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-list-failed (1),
.BR lightning-node-payment-count (1)
